(22, '&lt;p&gt;Time: 2020-07-23 19:15:48&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;date&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;comment&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If the font you are using is not installed on the user\'s computer, your website will revert to a generic font that was not part of your original design. This is very unfriendly for the UI design and user experience of the web page. If you want to keep your website design and visual brand consistent, then using web safe fonts ensures that your website is exactly what you expected to display on different devices.&lt;/p&gt;', NULL, '1', '793794', '786513', NULL, '2020-07-23 17:49:53', '2020-07-23 17:49:53'),
