hlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(41, 98, 255);&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. G Suite customers may see some changes to Google+ features related to the consumer Google+ shutdown. You can find more details&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.google.com/a/answer/9229693?hl=en_GB&amp;amp;authuser=0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(41, 98, 255);&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;or you can talk to your&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://support.google.com/a/answer/6208960?hl=en_GB&amp;amp;authuser=0&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; style=&quot;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(41, 98, 255);&quot;&gt;G Suite administrator&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;to learn more.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;', '1', '460845', 'Google+ is no longer available for consumer (personal) and brand accounts From all of us on the Google+ tea', 'Google+ is no longer available for consumer (personal) and brand accountsFrom all of us on the Google+ team,thank you for making Google+ s...', '11', '34', '77', 'Harvard', '2020/07/30 17:00', NULL, '2020-07-24 07:31:26', '2020-07-24 07:31:26'),
